Turtle.nextLevel: alert - This is displayed when the user solves the level, inviting them to precede to the next level of difficulty.
Turtle.finalLevelMsg: alert - This is displayed when the user solves the most difficult level.

Maze.tooFewBlocksMsg: alert - The user has not completed the level, is using all of the necessary types of blocks, but needs more of these types of blocks to complete the level.
Turtle.tryAgain: button - Closes the dialog and stays on the current level
Turtle.continue: button - Closes the dialog and continues to the next level
